<h3 id="_creating_the_leadtime_to_ship_property" class="discrete">Creating the leadtime to ship property</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can transfer the leadtime to ship for every variation. The leadtime to ship is the time in days that a seller needs from the order acceptance to the shipping registration. You can transfer a whole number between 1 and 45.</p>
</div>
